DISTRICT FUNDS); CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR; CALIFORNIA -- EDUCATION; CALIFORNIA -- 
FINANCES; CALIFORNIA -- SUITS; LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; PROFICIENCY TESTS; 
MALATHION; PEST CONTROL; HEALTH HAZARDS; STATUTE OF LIMITATIONS; VETOES; 
