in the 10-kilometer race. ; Photo, Monica Lawrence and her 4-month-old son, 
Daniel, wait for Robert Lawrence to finish race. GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, COLOR, John Voracek bares message for deployed Marines. ; Photo, 
COLOR, Participants in the Leatherneck Run of the Runways at the El Toro Marine 
base do just that. 
