Frank Fry Jr. 
</P>
<P>
Age: 65. 
</P>
<P>
Occupation: Retired department manager at Vons. 
</P>
<P>
Background: Has served on the City Council for 20 years; served a term as mayor 
beginning in 1978; current mayor pro tem. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Wants better preparation of the budget and more communication between 
mayor and council. 
</P>
