<P>
Sallie Mae Will Take Over Loan Program: The U.S. Department of Education said 
it plans to turn over the $9-billion portfolio of a financially troubled 
student-loan guarantee agency to Sallie Mae, the Student Loan Marketing Assn. 
</P>
