<DOCNO> LA100190-0108 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 286044 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 1, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 9; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
33 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Misspelling -- The name of actress Laurie Prange was misspelled and Richard 
Eden was misidentified in a caption accompanying the review of "A Streetcar 
Named Desire" in Thursday's Calendar. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
